My observations, importantly, apply to the wrong footed cannabis managements, who, in their rosy forecasts, led retail investors off the cliff. Look at the repeated guidedowns, but, even more important, the magnitude of said guidedowns. As a proxy look at Ayr Wellness.

Respectfully it has been the cannabis bulls that have failed to accurately present and analyze the fundamentals that have led to a -85% drawdown in $MSOS. This is not about hating or a conspiracy - its about analyzing - and most of the cannabis bulls will admit to that deficiency
